{
  "texts": [
    "ChLinkLockRevolute.Initialize requires a full frame (position + orientation); supplying raw vectors is semantically wrong and brittle across versions. 3.",
    "World modeling errors.",
    "No explicit fixed ground body is created and gravity is left implicit, making anchor references ill-defined and results non-reproducible. 4.",
    "Frame/axis specification mistakes.",
    "The revolute axis is inconsistent with planar motion (should be Z for XY-plane dynamics), and anchor orientations are omitted, leaving joint axes underdetermined. 5."
  ]
}